=== Loi giai tu luan ===

Thong so: n = 5, k = 3, r = 2
g(x) = x^2 + x + 1

STT  m(bin)      m(x)           c(bin)
------------------------------------------------------------
0    000         0              00000
1    001         x^2            11100
2    010         x              01110
3    011         x^2 + x        10010
4    100         1              00111
5    101         x^2 + 1        11011
6    110         x + 1          01001
7    111         x^2 + x + 1    10101

Ket qua: d_min = 2, phat hien 1 loi, sua 0 loi
